### Admin — trigger ML retrain from MongoDB
@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000
@adminToken = YOUR_ADMIN_JWT

### Training status (via Express → Flask)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/ml/training-status
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### Force retrain
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/ml/retrain
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "force": true,
  "auto": false
}

###

### Auto retrain (only if enough new records)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/ml/retrain
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "force": false,
  "auto": true
}
